## üé® Design Principles Applied

Based on authentic Finnish design research:

### Core Values
- **Extreme Simplicity**: Remove all unnecessary elements
- **Abundant White Space**: 90% of the interface is breathing room
- **Functional Beauty**: Every element serves a clear purpose
- **Neutral Palette**: Soft grays, minimal color
- **Clean Typography**: Thin weights, generous spacing
- **No Decoration**: No shadows, borders, or ornamental elements

### Visual Language
- **Text-only interactions**: No heavy buttons, just text links
- **Opacity for state**: Locked modes shown via reduced opacity (40%)
- **Minimal indicators**: Thin underlines, small dots instead of avatars
- **Sharp corners**: No border-radius (90¬∞ angles for purity)
- **Hairline borders**: 1px when absolutely necessary

