## ‚ú® Interaction Patterns

### Hover States
- **Text links**: Subtle underline appears
- **Mode labels**: No change (click only)
- **Menu items**: Underline appears

### Active States
- **Mode selector**: Thin 1px underline
- **Buttons**: None (text links don't have pressed states)

### Disabled States
- **Locked modes**: 40% opacity
- **No cursor change**: Maintains simplicity

### Focus States
- **Keyboard navigation**: Thin 1px outline in accent color
- **No heavy focus rings**: Keeps minimal aesthetic

