## üîÑ Comparison: Before vs After

### Original Design (Material Design 3)
- Rounded corners (12-20px)
- Background cards and containers
- Filled buttons with shadows
- Segmented button controls
- Brand colors and logos
- Icons and emojis
- Hover elevation effects

### Ultra-Minimalist Design (Finnish)
- Sharp corners (0px)
- No backgrounds or cards
- Text links only
- Plain text labels
- Neutral grays only
- No icons or decoration
- Underline on hover only

**Philosophy Shift**:
- From "visually rich" ‚Üí "visually calm"
- From "guided user" ‚Üí "trusted user"
- From "decorated" ‚Üí "essential"

