## üõ†Ô∏è Implementation Notes

### CSS Simplification

**Remove**:
- All `border-radius` properties
- All `box-shadow` properties
- All background colors (except white)
- All padding on buttons
- All container elements

**Keep**:
- Minimal padding (32px outer)
- Thin borders (1px hairline)
- Opacity for states
- Text underlines for active/hover

### HTML Simplification

**Before** (Material Design):
```html
<button class="md-filled-button">
  <span class="button-text">Sign In</span>
</button>
```

**After** (Finnish Minimal):
```html
<a href="#" class="link">sign in</a>
```

### Accessibility Considerations

- **Contrast ratios**: Still meet WCAG AA (4.5:1 minimum)
- **Touch targets**: Text links need 48px clickable area
- **Keyboard nav**: Focus outlines remain visible
- **Screen readers**: Semantic HTML unchanged

